Cell.Text: G|I'm sorry I disturbed you. Although it's a pressing matter for me, I'll seek help from someone else.

Node.Caption: ssg10ALostPetNotMeetingOwner: Sorry, I can't talk right now. I'm busy.

Cell.Text: Greetings again, my friend! Have you come back to help me?

I have been wandering up and down this road looking for my dear sweet pet. | We only just recently came to Skyrim, and I’m afraid the excitement was too much for her. | We had only just spied the docks when she jumped over the side and swam ashore. I don’t suppose you’ve seen her? | She’s wearing a lovely black collar and harness.
I am sorry to hear that...

Node.Caption: ssg20ALostPetNotSeen: I haven’t seen any animals wearing a collar like that.

Cell.Text: In fact I did spy a cave not to far from here where I fear she may have taken refuge. | I would investigate myself, but sadly I noticed signs of animals outside the cave, and I have nothing to protect myself with. | Now that I look at you, you seem quite skilled. | Could I impose upon you to accompany me to recover my pet, or at least her remains so that she can be properly laid to rest?
[S] G|Thank you gracious hero! Please follow me, this way.
[S] G|I have only ever called her ‘Pet. She was muzzled when I saw her last, so you shouldn't worry about being bit. Please, allow me to show you the way.

Node.Caption: ssg50ALostPetWhatsHerName: Very well. What’s her name? I’d hate to have her bite me thinking me a stranger.

Cell.Text: Of course I wouldn’t think of enlisting your aid without compensation. I would be happy to offer you 100 gold after her recovery. | Or if I could persuade such a competent companion to accompany me to meet with my friends, I’m certain we can provide you with a great deal more!

Node.Caption: ssg40ALostPetWhatsInItForMe: This seems like a too much effort for just a pet. What’s in it for me?

Cell.Text: [S] G|Then please follow me, this way.

Node.Caption: ssg50ALostPet100GoldSure: 100 Gold for a Pet? Sure why not!

Cell.Text: [S] G|A pity, but I cannot find fault in what you say. I suppose I will just have to hurry to the inn without her. Good Day.

Node.Caption: ssg50ALostPetBetterEyeOnNextPet: You should keep a better eye on your next pet. Goodbye.

Cell.Text: I fear you may be correct...

Node.Caption: ssg20ALostPetProbablyEaten: She’s probably been eaten by now.

Cell.Text: She’s a beautiful creature of a strong Imperial stock. I would hate to lose her…

Node.Caption: ssg20ALostPetPossibly: Possibly, what manner of animal is she?
